
Description: A few RapidSMS apps.
Licence: Public Domain

##########
# INSTALL
##########

* FIXTURES
    Some apps may require some datas in the DB to work.
    Import the content of the fixtures subfolder if applicable.

    Example:
        $ ./manage.py loaddata apps/billboard/fixtures/*.json

#################
# ChildCount-2.0
#################
Installation - develop
------------
$ sudo aptitude install gettext git-core python python-pybabel python-reportlab python-serial python-setuptools python-tz pdftk python-matplotlib python-xlwt python-mysqldb python-sqlite3

$ sudo easy_install pep8

$ sudo locale-gen fr_FR.UTF-8
$ sudo locale-gen en_US.UTF-8


#############
# Deployment
#############
$ cd ~
$ git clone git://github.com/mvpdev/rapidsms-impl.git install
$ ./install/deploy.py -c ./install/childcount-2.0/install.ini
$ cp ./install/childcount-2.0/local.ini sms/

